<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="belt-n">belt <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /belt/    美 /belt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>腰带；皮带；地带：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>green belt</strong>
绿化带</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fasten the seat / safety belts</strong>
系上安全带</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Belt and Road
一带一路（“丝绸之路经济带和21世纪海上丝绸之路”的简称）</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="tighten-ones-belt">tighten one’s belt</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[非正式用语] 勒紧裤腰带过日子</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>belted /'beltɪd/ adj   </p></div>